    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Carbon prints in which the transfer paper is sensitized when placed in contact with a silver bromide print. The term is generally used for colored carbro prints, but monochrome carbro prints also exist.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
